tte flere restriksjoner p\u00e5 dem, slik at teknologien kan bli til velsignelse og til st\u00f8tte \u2013 og ikke hinder for l\u00e6ringsarbeidet.", "Frustrert elev (19)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "meninger|snakkut"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "48cabea065486eb090911018d3d515ddd0b2e17b38573a00fb6137478763ecaf"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-10T07:49:49.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Les innlegget fra en frustrert 19-\u00e5ring."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2124816.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/skole-pc"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/0dea8db77e007ee6b90bb83c8422991cd9de309f.jpg?5946d96d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Skole-pc \u2013 er det et hinder for l\u00e6ring? -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "0dea8db77e007ee6b90bb83c8422991cd9de309f"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["meninger", "snakk ut", "leder"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "meninger,snakk ut,leder"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["meninger", "snakkut"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["skole-pc", "l\u00e6ring"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["meninger", "meninger/snakkut"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2124816.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/skole-pc"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Skole-pc &ndash; er det et hinder for l\u00e6ring?"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/snakkut/article1739565.ece